<task id="tdevdeploy19136" xml:lang="en-us">
<title>Deploying the database on the read-only media</title>
<shortdesc>To deploy the database on read-only media, perform the following
steps.</shortdesc>
<prolog><metadata>
<keywords><indexterm>Read-only databases<indexterm>deploying</indexterm></indexterm>
</keywords>
</metadata></prolog>
<taskbody>
<steps>
<step><cmd>Move the database directory to the read-only media, including the
necessary subdirectory directories (<i>log</i> and <i>seg0</i>) and the file <codeph><i>service.properties</i></codeph>.</cmd>
</step>
<step><cmd>Use the database as usual, except that you will not be able to
insert or update any data in the database or create or drop dictionary objects.</cmd>
</step>
</steps>
<result></result>
</taskbody>
</task>
